    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/e8e845fca660c07d7ce0e3bdaa35538c.gif?t=1765235894\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/e8e845fca660c07d7ce0e3bdaa35538c.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>拥有独特武器、能力和天赋的英雄<br></li><li>超过70种武器<br></li><li>武器融合系统<br></li><li>超过200种被动能力来构建您的技能组合<br></li><li>种族能力<br></li><li>宠物<br></li><li>符文<br></li><li>兽园<br></li><li>超过20小时的内容<br></li><li>拥有独特能力的首领<br></li><li>成千上万的可解锁物品<br></li><li>长时间的角色发展<br></li><li>在Steam Deck上完美运行<br></li><li>支持超宽屏<br></li><li>昼夜循环<br></li><li>无尽模式</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开始</strong></h2>白天狩猎，晚上被猎杀！与怪异的怪物战斗，它们会在晚上吓到你！通过收集来自世界各地的遗物、魔宠来强化你的英雄。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>昼夜循环</strong></h2>寻找仅在夜间生成的遗物和供应商。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.webm?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/ff32b5338468af57c28369da04175ea1.mp4?t=1765235894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>天气事件</strong></h2>做好准备！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a8d73bdba79e6492c50e0664.poster.avif?t=1765235894\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181720/extras/25edd202a